select 
CAST(MAX_SID AS BIGINT)               AS llave_tipo_origen  ,
CAST('axis' AS CHARACTER VARYING(30)) AS sistema_origen,
cast(cod_origen AS BIGINT) AS cod_origen,
cast(descripcion_origen AS CHARACTER VARYING(1000)) AS descripcion_origen
from 
(
select 1 as cod_origen ,'Contactos-Siniestr' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 2 as cod_origen ,'Contactos-Tesoreri' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 3 as cod_origen ,'Contactos-Web' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 4 as cod_origen ,'Contactos-Suscripcion' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 5 as cod_origen ,'Contactos-Sin Origen' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 6 as cod_origen ,'Siniestros Inspecciones' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 7 as cod_origen ,'Siniestros' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 8 as cod_origen ,'Portal Clientes' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 9 as cod_origen ,'Consulta Reclamos' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 10 as cod_origen ,'Asistencias' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 11 as cod_origen ,'Proveedor Externos' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 12 as cod_origen ,'Twilio' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 13 as cod_origen ,'Salesforce' as descripcion_origen
Union
select 14 as cod_origen ,'BPM' as descripcion_origen
)
LEFT JOIN
    (   SELECT
            MAX(llave_tipo_origen) AS MAX_SID
        FROM
            data_clientes_cl.cdm_cl_dim_tipo_origen_t ) LKP
ON
    1 = 1
